{"tid":1862423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天瑞邨居民聚集不滿未封深圳灣口岸　防暴警放催淚彈","createTime":"2020-02-04T15:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T02:56:21.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4c92612cd90ddf537a7314baa3219ec96ed0c0dd","tid":1862423,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"天水圍天瑞邨晚上有居民聚集，抗議政府未有封閉深圳灣口岸，大批防暴警員到場，舉黑旗警告，在天瑞商場外發射十多枚催淚彈及橡膠子彈，亦曾施放胡椒噴霧，現場響起火警鐘。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區議員伍健偉在社交專頁表示，被橡膠子彈擊中背部，正接受急救。另外，有理大編委記者表示，被橡膠子彈擊中右手手臂，亦有多名記者表示被胡椒噴霧噴中，有記者被截查，其後放行。"},{"pid":"47684963fe602174e9d934f62f422975ff7b8bb8","tid":1862423,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1506668_1_L_20200204230736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1506668_1_L_20200204230736.jpg&h=017ec6ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78428c5fce9e0e8edc3b74eb1b11ea07205f6220","tid":1862423,"uid":156327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:21:35.000Z","msg":"仆街軍政府"},{"pid":"083edf69db980b25f9b27e0de88416851d35f7f4","tid":1862423,"uid":297997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n香港已經全面公安化"},{"pid":"2011d0ea6afff7da9147f3c94bb0cb237ba1e2c9","tid":1862423,"uid":182061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"而家呢班區議員真係為民請命"},{"pid":"3527a9738d586cd36afaba528bbef9933cdd38f0","tid":1862423,"uid":266755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"47684963fe602174e9d934f62f422975ff7b8bb8","tid":1862423,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T15:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1506668_1_L_20200204230736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1506668_